Name: Pointer tool

Synonyms: pointer tool, arrow tool

Type: glossary

Description:
<tool|Tool> used in the LiveCode <development environment> to select, move,
and resize <control|controls>.

When the Pointer tool is being used, the <cursor> is in the shape of an
arrow. 

References: development environment (glossary), tool (glossary),
cursor (glossary), control (glossary)

